OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775761868
OL,3,CIran's Deputy Foreign Minister tells
OL,4,CITV News 'the Strait of Hormuz is open'
OL,6,FDr Saeed Khatibzadeh told ITV News
OL,7,FIran was committed to peace in the
OL,8,FMiddle East but was sceptical of the
OL,9,F"other side"
OL,11,FThe Strait of Hormuz is open, Iran's
OL,12,FDeputy Foreign Minister told me this
OL,13,Fmorning.
OL,15,FAny civilian vessel can pass with
OL,16,Fguidance from the Iranian authorities.
OL,18,FThat guidance is necessary because, as
OL,19,Fpart of this war, Iran mined the
OL,20,Fcrucial waterway, and those mines
OL,21,Fremain, he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
