OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775761868
OL,3,CIran's Deputy Foreign Minister tells
OL,4,CITV News 'the Strait of Hormuz is open'
OL,6,FThe Iranians have the maps and
OL,7,Flocations for safe passage.
OL,9,FWhy does this matter? Because Iran's
OL,10,Fcontrol of the Strait during this war
OL,11,Fhas caused a global energy and
OL,12,Feconomic crisis.
OL,14,FThe passage of vessels is in part what
OL,15,Fhas pushed the United States to the
OL,16,Fnegotiating table.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775761868
OL,3,CIran's Deputy Foreign Minister tells
OL,4,CITV News 'the Strait of Hormuz is open'
OL,6,FHowever, the Strait being open is
OL,7,FIran's greatest power and key to any
OL,8,Fceasefire. If the Americans and
OL,9,FIsraelis don't agree to Iran's key
OL,10,Fdemands, the Strait can be closed
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,FAnd passage is only with Iran's
OL,14,Fagreement, however open it might be.
OL,16,F"Anybody who communicates with the
OL,17,FIranian authority has got permission
OL,18,Fto pass," Dr Saeed Khatibzadeh told me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
