OL,3,CIran's Deputy Foreign Minister tells
OL,4,CITV News 'the Strait of Hormuz is open'
OL,6,FCentral to Iran's demands is a
OL,7,Fceasefire in Lebanon, too. Yesterday's
OL,8,Fwave of attacks by Israel, resulting
OL,9,Fin the deaths of almost 200 people,
OL,10,Fhas pushed this 14-day pause to its
OL,11,Flimit.
OL,13,FDr Khatibzadeh said: "I have all the
OL,14,Freasons to be sceptical regarding the
OL,15,Fintention of the other side, but more
OL,16,Fthan that, as we are seeing, Israelis
OL,17,Fare violating, the grave violation is
OL,18,Fhappening right now in Lebanon,
OL,19,Fyesterday was a massacre."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
