OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775761868
OL,3,CIran's Deputy Foreign Minister tells
OL,4,CITV News 'the Strait of Hormuz is open'
OL,6,FThe deputy foreign minister also had a
OL,7,Ffew words for the UK and how it had
OL,8,Fmanaged the conflict.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FHe said the British government should
OL,16,F"face the facts", adding the UK
OL,17,Fpermitted American B2 bombers to
OL,18,Flaunch strikes on Iran from RAF bases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
