OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775761868
OL,3,CIran's Deputy Foreign Minister tells
OL,4,CITV News 'the Strait of Hormuz is open'
OL,6,F"It is nonsense that in a war, a
OL,7,Fcountry says that I'm not part of this
OL,8,Fwar, but I provide all the
OL,9,Finfrastructure for you to start an
OL,10,Foffensive operation against another
OL,11,Fcountry," he said.
OL,13,FThe UK government has insisted that
OL,14,Fpermitting the US to use British
OL,15,Fmilitary sites to launch strikes on
OL,16,FIran has only been for defensive
OL,17,Foperations.
OL,19,FBut in the eyes of the Iranians, there
OL,20,Fis no distinction between defensive
OL,21,Fand offensive operations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
